279
00:18:43,310 --> 00:18:44,480
Mở cửa ra nào, Finney.

280
00:18:50,360 --> 00:18:51,400
Chào.

281
00:18:51,450 --> 00:18:52,570
Chào. Anh sao rồi, Buck?

282
00:18:54,410 --> 00:18:55,410
